pageProduct.name: Swisse Ultinatal Breastfeeding Support 90 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Ultinatal Breastfeeding Support is a premium quality formula specifically tailored to help increase breastmilk production and provide nutritional support for mother & baby during the breastfeeding cycle.

Swisse Ultinatal Breastfeeding Support is a premium quality formula specifically tailored to help increase
breastmilk production and provide nutritional support for mother & baby during the breastfeeding cycle.
Increases Breastmilk Production: Formulated with fenugreek, used in traditional Western herbal medicine as a
galactogouge to help increase the production of breastmilk.
Reduces Tiredness & Fatigue: B group vitamins including activated B12 (as mecobalamin) help support healthy
energy levels and contribute to reduction of tiredness and fatigue.
Nutrient Replenishment: Vitamins B3, B5, B6 and B12 can help support increased dietary nutritional needs during breastfeeding.

Size: 90 Tablets

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If you are concerned about the health of yourself or your baby, or if symptoms persist, consult your healthcare practitioner.

IMPORTANT INFORMATION

No added lactose, gluten, yeast, egg, soy, artificial colours or artificial flavours.

Ingredients

EACH TABLET CONTAINS:
FENUGREEK (Trigonella foenum-graecum dry seed extract 200 mg) equiv. dry seed 2 g
METHYL VITAMIN B12 (mecobalamin) 5 mcg
VITAMIN B1 (thiamine from thiamine hydrochloride 5.61 mg) 5 mg
VITAMIN B2 (riboflavin) 5 mg
VITAMIN B3 (nicotinamide) 6 mg
VITAMIN B5 (pantothenic acid from calcium pantothenate 5.46 mg) 5 mg
VITAMIN B6 (pyridoxine from pyridoxine hydrochloride 6.08 mg) 5 mg

Directions

DIRECTIONS FOR USE - ADULT DOSAGE:
Three tablets daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
